Quickly import people and organizations into your Decile Hub funnels. Just launch the extension and AI does the rest.

Please note: You must have a Decile Hub account to use this extension. You will need an API key, which can be found under: Settings > API.

As always, we build Hub for you, so feedback is welcome! This is a first generation product, so let us know if you find any opportunities to make it better.
